\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 15. C. neapolitanum} (Ten.) Ten.,{\i  Fl. Neap. Prodr. App. Quinta} 11 (1826) (incl. {\i C. longifolium} Cast., {\i C. kochii} Parl.). Leaves (2-)3-4, 14-26 cm × 10-30(-40) mm, linear-lanceolate. Perianth-segments usually 30-45 × 7-12 mm. Anthers yellow. Flowering August to September (-October). 2n = 140.{\i  Mediterranean region, Portugal.} Co Ga Gr Hs It Ju Lu Sa.
\par

