\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 16. C. lusitanum} Brot., {\i Phyt. Lusit.}{\b  2}: 211 (1827). Leaves 4-5, 18-35 cm × 20-40 mm, linear-lanceolate. Perianth-segments 40-60 × 6-14 mm. Anthers blackish-purple to pale purplish-pink or yellow. Flowering September to November. 2n = 106.{\i  S.W. Europe, extending to C. Italy.} ?Bl Hs It Lu.
\par

